<L>__{int & exterior berg apartment. day 1959. a sunny day in march. michael's bed has been moved}
<A>__{beside open windows so he can profit from the weak sun. he is sitting up, working on his stamp collection. carla is moving round behind him, tidying the room.}
<C>__{carla}
<D>__{how are you feeling?}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{better. by the way, i meant to tell you, the day i got ill... a woman helped me. a woman in the street.}
<C>__{carla}
<D>__{she helped you?}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{yes. she brought me home.}
<C>__{carla}
<D>__{do you have her address?}
